creator: CSCMobi App Studio
descriptionHtml:
Have you ever needed to measure something but didn't have a tape measure handy? When you wanted to know the dimensions of an object without touching it? Or wondered if a new furniture would fit in your room or not? If your answer is yes, then you need this AR Ruler Cam: Photo Measure app.

AR Ruler: Tape Measure Mobile App is a smart and easy way to measure anything with your smartphone. Using the power of augmented reality (AR), you can turn your camera into a virtual ruler and measure distances, angles, areas, volumes, and more. All you need is your phone and a flat surface to start measuring.

FEATURES:
📏 AR Ruler: Measure linear sizes in cm, m, mm, inches, feet, or yards
📏 On-screen Ruler: Measure small objects directly on your phone screen
📏 Angle: Measure the angle between two lines or surfaces
📏 Volume: Measure the volume of any 3D object by fitting a cube around it
📏 Path: Measure the length of a path by tracing it with your phone
📏 Height: Measure the height of an object relative to a recognized surface

HOW TO USE:
📐 Select the tool you want to use
📐 Adjust your camera and detect a plane
📐 Measure by tapping on the screen or moving your phone
📐 Capture and save your measurements

Don't wait any longer. Download AR Ruler Cam: Photo Measure today and discover a new way to measure the world around you!
